This is a dual-use license.
If you're not into mystical traditions, it functions as an MIT license.
Of you are, and aspire to world peace, it comes with a blessing.
The second line of files covered by the latter case are tagged with:
"This code is a gift to the divine".
There is no legal requirement to not misuse it other than "God will get you".

